作、影响老板对自己的态度、甚至可能会导致被辞退，越来越多的职场年轻人有了「请假耻辱」，有事 / 因病想要请假时，内心会产生焦虑和愧疚，导致害怕甚至不敢请假。"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "73 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/629245616"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Iu5zX/tTK34o2EAMaCTEwMjExMDk0MSD8p6KqBjAAODVAEXIJNjI5MjQ1NjE2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "18_1699538561.874965", "card_id": "Q_629609622", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 41}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "这个 11.11 有没有更省钱的买手机攻略？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "最近各大厂商都有新品手机发布，赶在这个热闹的 11.11 即有新品抢购，又有老机型优惠，大家有什么购机新攻略可以分享的，让我们这些打工人们体验一把轻松换手机的快乐。"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "71 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/629609622"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Iu5zX/tTK34o2EAMaCTEwMjE5MTYyOSDo7bKqBjAAODRAEnIJNjI5NjA5NjIyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "19_1699538561.875340", "card_id": "Q_629414943", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 47}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "中山二院博士黄某所患的「SMARCB1 缺失型癌」有多严重？为什么说很罕见？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "中山医院通报：黄某，女，2017 年至 2022 年在我院攻读博士学位，此间在乳腺肿瘤中心实验室学习，2022 年 7 月博士毕业后入职我院乳腺外科，从事临床工作。2023 年 10 月被确诊患胰腺癌并接受手术，目前情况稳定。 网传报告中诊断是「符合胰腺 SMARCB1 /INI1 缺失型未分化癌」。中山二院深夜通报乳腺外科多人患癌事件 _ 央广网 「SMARCB1 缺失」「未分化」这些都是什么意思，有多严重？以及有什么能够帮助她吗？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-2cb62908d1a1d80944cb1b0f87cf4042_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "59 万热度", "font_color": "", "b